Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.31,ED_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}獨自在意著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:21.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur(5)}せつないだけ
